{
  "nodes": [
    {"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# AI 外呼流程管理 · 业务全景\n基于当前代码实现梳理（控制面 / 调度面 / 媒体面 / 对话执行面）","x":-120,"y":-760,"width":720,"height":140,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"legend","type":"text","text":"## 图例\n- 紫色：流程配置与任务控制（NestJS）\n- 蓝色：可靠调度与电话网络\n- 绿色：实时对话执行（Python）\n- 黄色：业务动作与数据回写\n- 红色：失败、重试与终止分支","x":650,"y":-760,"width":470,"height":190},

    {"id":"g_design","type":"group","label":"① 流程设计与发布","x":-180,"y":-500,"width":1200,"height":650,"color":"6"},
    {"id":"operator","type":"text","text":"## 运营人员\n在 Dashboard 中创建、编辑外呼流程","x":-120,"y":-400,"width":250,"height":120,"color":"6"},
    {"id":"editor","type":"text","text":"## 流程编辑器\n五类节点：\nStart → Dialog → Decision → Action → End\n\nDialog：script / question / AI\nDecision：condition / intent\nAction：transfer / SMS / CRM / API","x":210,"y":-450,"width":330,"height":280,"color":"6"},
    {"id":"validate","type":"text","text":"## 保存草稿并校验\n校验入口、连线、节点配置和可达性\n状态：draft","x":610,"y":-390,"width":300,"height":150,"color":"6"},
    {"id":"publish","type":"text","text":"## 发布流程\nNestJS 创建不可变 TaskFlowVersion 快照\n版本号递增，状态变为 published\n运行中的任务不会被后续编辑影响","x":610,"y":-140,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"6"},

    {"id":"g_task","type":"group","label":"② 创建任务与派发","x":1100,"y":-500,"width":1340,"height":650,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"create_task","type":"text","text":"## 创建外呼任务\nDashboard / API 提交：\n被叫号码、场景、变量、scheduledAt、flowId","x":1160,"y":-420,"width":300,"height":180,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"lock_version","type":"text","text":"## 锁定流程版本\nNestJS 解析该流程最新已发布版本\n写入 flowVersionId\n任务状态：pending\n记录 task.created 事件","x":1540,"y":-420,"width":300,"height":190,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"dispatch","type":"text","text":"## 触发派发\nPOST /tasks/:id/dispatch\n当前由 Dashboard / API 显式触发\n\n注意：scheduledAt 已存储，但当前代码未见自动扫描到期任务的调度器","x":1920,"y":-450,"width":400,"height":250,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"transaction","type":"text","text":"## 单事务落库\n1. Task → calling，attemptCount +1\n2. 创建 CallAttempt\n3. 记录 call.dispatch_requested\n4. 写 OutboxEvent（含去重键）","x":1540,"y":-120,"width":350,"height":210,"color":"4"},

    {"id":"g_delivery","type":"group","label":"③ 可靠调度与电话接通","x":2520,"y":-500,"width":1540,"height":650,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"worker","type":"text","text":"## Outbox Worker\n轮询 pending 事件 → 抢占租约\n校验 payload → 调用 FreeSWITCH ESL\n避免业务事务与外部调用耦合","x":2580,"y":-420,"width":330,"height":200,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"originate","type":"text","text":"## FreeSWITCH originate\n使用 attemptId 作为 origination_uuid\n经 SIP Gateway 呼叫客户\n接受后记录 call.dispatch_accepted","x":3000,"y":-420,"width":330,"height":190,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"answered","type":"text","text":"## 客户是否接听？","x":3420,"y":-380,"width":250,"height":100,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"audio_fork","type":"text","text":"## 应答后建立媒体流\nDialplan 执行 mod_audio_fork\n双向 WebSocket：\n客户 PCM → Voice Agent\nTTS PCM → FreeSWITCH → 客户","x":3730,"y":-430,"width":280,"height":220,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"dispatch_retry","type":"text","text":"## 派发失败\n指数退避后回到 pending\n记录 retrying 事件\n达到最大次数：Task / Attempt → failed","x":2840,"y":-120,"width":350,"height":190,"color":"1"},
    {"id":"no_answer","type":"text","text":"## 未接 / 呼叫异常\n目标状态模型支持：\nno_answer / failed / cancelled\n需由电话事件回传驱动状态更新","x":3420,"y":-100,"width":330,"height":180,"color":"1"},

    {"id":"g_runtime","type":"group","label":"④ Python Voice Agent 执行对话流程","x":4140,"y":-500,"width":1640,"height":650,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"context","type":"text","text":"## 拉取任务上下文\nVoice Agent 用 FreeSWITCH UUID（即 attemptId）请求 NestJS\n获得场景、变量和锁定的 flowVersion 快照","x":4200,"y":-430,"width":340,"height":210,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"session","type":"text","text":"## 创建会话\n初始化 system prompt、变量、工具集\n有 flowVersion：进入 FlowExecutor\n无 flowVersion：兼容内置场景模式","x":4620,"y":-430,"width":330,"height":210,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"dialog","type":"text","text":"## Dialog 节点\n模板填充 → TTS 播放\n等待客户语音 → ASR\n支持静默重试、打断和 AI 回复\n双方文本逐轮回写 TranscriptTurn","x":5030,"y":-450,"width":340,"height":240,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"decision","type":"text","text":"## Decision 节点\ncondition：表达式判断\nintent：关键词优先，LLM 分类兜底\n按边标签选择下一节点","x":5420,"y":-410,"width":300,"height":190,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"next_node","type":"text","text":"循环执行下一节点\n受最大步数保护","x":5030,"y":-100,"width":250,"height":100,"color":"3"},

    {"id":"g_action","type":"group","label":"⑤ 动作执行与流程结束","x":5860,"y":-500,"width":1770,"height":650,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"action_choice","type":"text","text":"## Action 节点","x":5920,"y":-390,"width":230,"height":100,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"transfer","type":"text","text":"### 转人工\nVoice Agent → NestJS\nFreeSWITCH uuid_transfer\n记录 call.transferred\n最终 outcome = escalated","x":6230,"y":-450,"width":270,"height":200,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"sms_api","type":"text","text":"### SMS / API\nVoice Agent 请求 NestJS 入 Outbox\nWorker 可靠投递短信或 Webhook\n幂等键去重；失败自动重试\n记录 delivered / retrying / failed","x":6570,"y":-470,"width":330,"height":250,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"crm","type":"text","text":"### CRM\n由 Python 工具调度器直接执行\n结果可继续流程或触发转人工","x":6980,"y":-430,"width":260,"height":170,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"end","type":"text","text":"## End 节点\n可播放告别语\ncomplete：结束流程执行\nhangup：调用 NestJS → FreeSWITCH 挂断","x":7300,"y":-440,"width":280,"height":210,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"outcome","type":"text","text":"## 结果沉淀\n回写 outcome、intentTags、endedAt、duration\n保存录音地址（模型已预留）\nDashboard 查询任务、尝试记录、转写与事件时间线","x":6900,"y":-120,"width":420,"height":200,"color":"2"},

    {"id":"g_state","type":"group","label":"任务状态机（当前领域模型）","x":100,"y":300,"width":2520,"height":430,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"s_pending","type":"text","text":"pending\n等待派发","x":170,"y":440,"width":210,"height":100,"color":"4"},
    {"id":"s_calling","type":"text","text":"calling\n正在呼叫","x":520,"y":440,"width":210,"height":100,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"s_incall","type":"text","text":"in_call\n已接通","x":870,"y":440,"width":210,"height":100,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"s_completed","type":"text","text":"completed\n正常结束","x":1250,"y":370,"width":220,"height":100,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"s_failed","type":"text","text":"failed\n失败（可再次派发）","x":1250,"y":520,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"1"},
    {"id":"s_noanswer","type":"text","text":"no_answer\n无人接听（可再次派发）","x":1620,"y":520,"width":250,"height":110,"color":"1"},
    {"id":"s_cancelled","type":"text","text":"cancelled\n已取消","x":2000,"y":440,"width":220,"height":100,"color":"1"},
    {"id":"state_note","type":"text","text":"终态：completed / failed / no_answer / cancelled\n其中 failed、no_answer 允许重新进入 calling，形成新的 CallAttempt。","x":2260,"y":380,"width":300,"height":180},

    {"id":"g_boundary","type":"group","label":"系统职责边界","x":2780,"y":300,"width":2470,"height":430,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"b_nest","type":"text","text":"## NestJS（控制面）\n流程 CRUD / 校验 / 发布 / 版本快照\n任务状态机、CallAttempt、事件与转写持久化\nOutbox、幂等、外部动作投递\nFreeSWITCH 控制命令","x":2850,"y":390,"width":430,"height":230,"color":"6"},
    {"id":"b_python","type":"text","text":"## Python（对话执行面）\n实时音频处理、ASR / TTS / LLM\n按不可变流程快照遍历节点\n意图识别、工具调用、动作请求\n逐轮上报对话和最终结果","x":3380,"y":390,"width":420,"height":230,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"b_fs","type":"text","text":"## FreeSWITCH（电话与媒体面）\nSIP 外呼、通道 UUID、应答与挂断\n音频 fork、转人工、录音承载","x":3900,"y":390,"width":390,"height":190,"color":"5"},
    {"id":"b_db","type":"text","text":"## PostgreSQL（事实源）\nTaskFlow / Version / OutboundTask\nCallAttempt / TranscriptTurn / CallEvent\nOutboxEvent","x":4390,"y":390,"width":390,"height":190,"color":"2"},
    {"id":"b_rule","type":"text","text":"核心原则：NestJS 决定“执行哪一版、任务处于什么状态”；Python 决定“这一通电话如何实时对话”。","x":4850,"y":400,"width":330,"height":170,"color":"4"}
  ],
